headline.main: SINGAPORE'S UNITY BACKS HEAVY GUNS; Harmony Among People Greater Than in 80 Years as Artillery Opens on the Enemy FOOD IS STILL PLENTIFUL There Is Also Work for Everybody -- Retired Brokers Cultivate Vegetable Gardens

lead_paragraph: SINGAPORE, Feb. 2 -- Singapore sat down to a rationed dinner tonight with an orchestra of guns hurling tons of high explosives across Johore Strait.
